companies.name: Groq
companies.reason: Groq has entered into a non-exclusive licensing agreement with Nvidia for its AI inference technology. This collaboration enhances Nvidia's capabilities in AI and accelerates its dominance in the AI hardware market. Additionally, Groq is noted for unveiling the fastest AI inference performance for foundational large language models (LLMs).

companies.name: TravelSky Technology
companies.reason: TravelSky Technology is making headlines due to the extension of its Service Framework Agreement with its connected company, which enhances its service offerings in aviation technologies. Recently, however, its stock has faced a decline after it issued weaker-than-expected earnings guidance for 2023, which has led to concerns regarding its growth prospects.
